#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1194
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1797
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1043
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:745
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1108
msgid ""
"Orcs kidnapped me while I was studying the crypt. I'm writing my thesis on "
"the Crypt of the Sacred Blood. But I'm only beginning."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1112
msgid ""
"The orcs wanted me to translate what is written on those tombs. In the "
"meantime, they started to raise skeletons."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1116
msgid ""
"Those brainless thugs barely understand fire. How could they master "
"necromancy? This does not bode well, but I doubt we will learn more here."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1127
msgid "Do you know how to get out of here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1131
msgid "There is an exit north."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1142
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1828
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1066
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:764
msgid "Can we help you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1147
msgid "Actually, yes. Would you mind me coming with you?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1149
msgid "No, come with us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1164
msgid "Thank you. I didn’t like the idea of having to stay here by myself anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1168
msgid ""
"Lujeje is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a  collection, will "
"always be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you will not be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1172
msgid "You can now recruit initiates."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1177
msgid "Yes, I'm better by myself."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1181
msgid ""
"(angry) Alright. But don’t worry, I’m sure I’ll be fine, alone, with no "
"weapon and in the middle of the orcs and other monsters. Best regards!"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1195
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:652
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:894
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1776
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1929
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2121
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2209
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1377
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:779
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:967
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1142
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1346
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1527
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1973
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:641
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:722
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1526
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1940
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1188
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1336
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1274
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:876
msgid "Leave"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1212
msgid "Yes, let's quit this crypt."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1222
msgid "No, I have some more things to do before leaving the crypt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1231
msgid ""
"The crypt really is a mortal maze. I don't think we will be able to get out "
"of here alive."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=05_Reaching_Zei
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:33
msgid "Reaching Zei"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:80
msgid "Reach Zei with a hero"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:85
msgid "Defeat all orcish leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:434
msgid "I'm glad we are finally out of that crypt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:438
msgid ""
"However, I'm quite worried by what we have seen down there. Who would have "
"thought that orcs could master necromancy?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:442
msgid ""
"Anyway, we only need to go down this mountain and we will reach Zei. I hope "
"it is not too late to bring the message."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:452
msgid ""
"I would like to help you, but I would need a better staff and an armour. Can "
"you please lend me this?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:456
msgid "Sure, no problem. We have some items that we are not using."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:460
msgid "You can equip items on your other heroes the same way you equip Io."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:464
msgid "Do you know how to get to Zei from here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:468
msgid "There are two ways. We can either take the main road or the pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:472
msgid ""
"The main road goes north to avoid the mountains then go back south-west. "
"There is also a mountain road that goes north-west directly to Zei, but it "
"might not be faster as it is very narrow."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:489
msgid ""
"This is where the two roads split. The pass is north-west from here while the"
" main road continue north-east."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:506
msgid "South: Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:524
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:590
msgid "North: Zei"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:567
msgid "It is as free as one can be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:633
msgid "It is now free to attack whoever it wants."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:681
msgid "Free and evil."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:729
msgid "It's free. But I don't know if it's good for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:757
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:814
msgid ""
"With only a name given by a dying friend, our shattered hero is crossing "
"Zei’s doors, marked by fights."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:761
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:818
msgid ""
"Who could have then imagined that the arrival of a humble farmer was going to"
" change forever the future of the kingdom?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:773
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:902
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1422
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1461
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1555
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1517
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the orcs here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:797
msgid "That's it. We defeated the orcish leaders that were pillaging the region."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:801
msgid "I found the valuables they had accumulated."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:805
msgid ""
"I do not think we will be able to find their rightful owners, but let's keep "
"them. \n"
"We can now go to Zei without having to worry about what we leave behind us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:834
msgid ""
"There are too many orcs between us and Zei. The city has probably fallen "
"already. Everything is lost."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=06_Zei
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:4
msgid "Zei"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:24
msgid ""
"With only a name given by a dying friend, our shattered hero is crossing "
"Zei’s doors, marked by fights. \n"
"Who could have then imagined that the arrival of a humble farmer was going to"
" change forever the future of the kingdom?"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:52
msgid "Find and talk to Csia"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:69
msgid "Kill the monsters on the beach."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:81
msgid "Buy some food and find a way to carry it. You have $food_counter| food."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:93
msgid "Buy at least 5 food. You have $food_counter| food."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:98
msgid "Leave Zei to Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:299
msgid "Welcome to Zei, stranger."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:303
msgid ""
"You managed to clear yourself a path through this orcish jungle? I imagine "
"the hordes of savages that went through here last night continued to the "
"Arable Highlands."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Unfortunately they have. They butchered some of my friends before we were "
"able to stop them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:311
msgid ""
"I'm sorry for the loss of your friends. Please excuse us for this mess. We "
"have been unable to mend the hurts caused by the orcish waves."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:315
msgid ""
"I think most shops are open, but, because of the orc's looting, there must "
"not be much available."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:319
msgid "We will probably go look anyway. We have items to sell and gold to buy with."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:333
msgid "Excuse me. Do you happen to be Csia?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:337
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:816
msgid "Yes I am."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:341
msgid ""
"If you’re here to seek help, don’t count on it. What the orcs couldn’t take "
"was destroyed or burnt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:345
msgid ""
"They even burnt Reaper, my good old catapult… although it hadn’t thrown a "
"stone for so many years."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:378
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:838
msgid "What can I do for you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Excuse me, who are you exactly? I was only given your name by a dying friend "
"to come for help and I don't know much more."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:388
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:849
msgid "I'm Csia, mayor of Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:403
msgid "Don't worry about me. I have seen worse during the war."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:414
msgid "Do you have more information about what happened here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:418
msgid "Not much."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:422
msgid ""
"But believe in the experience of an old man: goblins were involved in this "
"orcish attack."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:426
msgid "Anyway, you should ask the other survivors. They might have heard something."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:437
msgid "Can we do anything to help ?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:441
msgid ""
"The guardian of Udxatfe must be informed of what happened. But I need all the"
" guards of Zei to defend the city. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:451
msgid ""
"You look like you can defend yourself. I need you to come with me and my men "
"to Udxatfe. Any problem with that?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:453
msgid "No, sir. I'm sure your experience will help us reach Udxatfe safely."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:468
msgid ""
"Hey, I’m glad to see there are still courageous young people. Give me five, "
"young boy!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:472
msgid ""
"It looks like the people you are travelling with are trusting you. I think I "
"will let you lead them, as long as you don't prove them wrong."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:485
msgid ""
"Csia is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a collection, will always "
"be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you won't be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:491
msgid "You can now recruit sergeants."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:496
msgid "We can do it by ourselves, sir. The city needs you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Meh, it’s not a bad thing. We need a hero to solve the problems here and "
"those aren’t any of your concern. Good luck!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:508
msgid ""
"My friends, I'm afraid my journey is not over. If I want to avenge Gu, I need"
" to go find Udxatfe's guardian to make sure nothing worse is happening in "
"Idaamub."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:512
msgid ""
"But you can't come with me. The farms need to be repaired and the fields to "
"be planted."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:517
msgid "We understand. We will take care of your farm and fields while you're away."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:522
msgid ""
"Had you not been here, we'd surely all be dead by now. It's the least we can "
"do."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:527
msgid "Here, take this gold. You'll need it more than us for your journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:535
msgid ""
"Thank you my friends and farewell. I'll come back as soon as I will have "
"avenged Gu."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:552
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Peasants and Woodsmen."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:556
msgid "Without the Woodsmen, we will have to buy food, and this will cost us gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:561
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/help.cfg:155
msgid ""
"You will lose 1 food at the beginning of each scenario. Bonus scenarios will "
"not cost you food.\n"
"If you have no food, every unit of yours will lose some HP at the beginning "
"of your turns.\n"
"Traders sell food, but you can also loot some on enemies.\n"
"You can check how much food you have by right-clicking anywhere on the map."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:571
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/help.cfg:166
msgid ""
"You will lose 1 food at the beginning of each scenario. Bonus scenarios will "
"not cost you food.\n"
"If you have no food, you will not be able to proceed to next scenario.\n"
"Traders sell food, but you can also loot some on enemies.\n"
"You can check how much food you have by right-clicking anywhere on the map."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:592
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1104
msgid "I will continue with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:596
msgid ""
"Based on what happened in the crypt, I hope to witness things that haven't "
"occurred since the War of Legions."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:602
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1114
msgid "I won't continue with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:606
msgid "It is too dangerous out there and I would only be a burden."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:610
msgid "I will pray for you saving us all."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:634
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Initiates."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:668
msgid ""
"You're the first farmer to come to our mill since the orcs began their "
"horrible massacre."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:672
msgid "I'm sorry, but we're not here to mill grain."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:676
msgid ""
"You didn't come to have your grain milled? If the orcs went all the way to "
"the Arable Highlands, horribly savage days await us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:680
msgid ""
"They emptied our granary, and then cut down the supply chain. We will only "
"have enough food for a week, best case."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:684
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1373
msgid "Can we do something to help you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:688
msgid ""
"I wanted to go to the beach to fish, but it seems the orcs left behind some "
"of those horrible mudcrawlers."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:692
msgid ""
"I begged the captain of the guard to help us clean the beach, but he doesn't "
"realize the seriousness of the situation. He won't reassign the guards on "
"duty at the doors until they have been repaired."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:696
msgid ""
"If you are brave enough to clean the beach (what I'm not capable of), it "
"would greatly help the citizens."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:706
msgid "Well, actually, we already got rid of them"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:711
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:756
msgid "Thank you so much. Now we won't starve to death."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:715
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:760
msgid ""
"Please take some food as a mark of appreciation. We don't need to spare it as"
" much now, thanks to you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:720
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:765
msgid "You receive 5 food."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:729
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1552
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2306
msgid "We will see what we can do."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:751
msgid ""
"That's it. We killed the mudcrawlers that were on the beach. You can fish "
"now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:781
msgid "Excuse me. You look in bad shape. What happened to you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:785
msgid ""
"The orcs set my house on fire. The crooks who teach the orcs how to raise "
"skeletons and set fire to brave people's houses deserve Emiijainu's torture."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:789
msgid ""
"As if their strike force was not devastating enough, those damned orcs "
"brought those horrible monsters from the highlands."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:793
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:691
msgid "Can we do something for you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:797
msgid ""
"You can't unburn my house, but if you could find the orcs and give them a "
"taste of their own medicine, that would be nice."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:811
msgid ""
"You're safe here for now: I think we left a bitter taste in orc's mouths "
"after the slaughter they suffered last night."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:861
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Black Hammer Forge. Orcs nearly stole everything from us but, "
"what's left, you won't find anywhere at a better price. What can I do for you"
" today?"
msgstr ""

