#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1274
msgid "The explosion opened a hole in the wall."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1313
msgid "What's this room?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1317
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1327
msgid "This is where we repair the carts."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1321
msgid "That explains all the tracks."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1354
msgid "I think I found the elevator."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1383
msgid "We don't have the time to fight rats. Let's go down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1395
msgid "The rats are dead. Let's go down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1416
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the rats here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1442
msgid ""
"Too many rats. We can't fight them and the orcs. We will have to find another"
" way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1448
msgid ""
"Too many orcs. We will never be able to reach Hufifa nor the exit of the "
"mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1462
msgid "The king of the rats is dead. Now, let's destroy the nest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1491
msgid "That's it. The rats should not bother us anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1497
msgid "That's it. The rats should not bother the dwarves anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=13_Miners_Life
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:6
msgid "Miners Life"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:52
msgid "Clean the dwarvish living quarters."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:708
msgid "Wow! It looks like there's a little welcoming commitee waiting for us. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:789
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1131
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1190
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1249
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:176
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:581
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:640
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:707
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:766
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:843
msgid "It opened a hole in the wall."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:831
msgid "The zone is cleared."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:835
msgid "So, Amin, tell us. Which way should we go?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:839
msgid "The next elevator is north-west."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:872
msgid "Look over there. This a mine worm. They dig galleries in the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:876
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:904
msgid "Be careful not to get hurt. They shoot poisonous stings."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:880
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:908
msgid "Life in the mines seems really dangerous."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:884
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:912
msgid "You don't say?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:890
msgid "What's this monstrosity?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:900
msgid "This a mine worm. They dig galleries in the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:918
msgid "It looks like a big worm."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:927
msgid "It went back into its hole. Who knows where it will reappear?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:947
msgid "There is a teleporting rune on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:951
msgid "It teleports the one walking on it somewhere else."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:955
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1014
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1056
msgid "I didn't know the dwarves possess this kind of knowledge."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:965
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1018
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1066
msgid "We don't. Those were already here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:969
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1022
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1070
msgid "The demons must have placed them then. Are they safe?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:973
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1026
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1074
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"Well, we are using them on a daily basis, so I would say they are. The only "
"problem is that you never know what's on the other side in advance."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:977
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1030
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1078
msgid ""
"I heard rumors of people merging with other beings inappropriately standing "
"on the receiving rune. But this one seems to have a protection against that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:981
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1034
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1082
msgid "Yes, they don't work if someone is standing on the other side."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:987
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1088
msgid ""
"This isn't safe magic. I heard rumors of people merging with other beings "
"inappropriately standing on the receiving rune. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:991
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1092
msgid "But this one seems to have a protection against that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1000
msgid "Look over there. This rune on the floor is a teleporting rune."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1004
msgid "It teleports the one walking on it to another rune further in the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1042
msgid "There is a rune drawn on the floor. What could it be?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1052
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1106
msgid "It is a teleporting rune. It teleports the one walking on it somewhere else."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1110
msgid "Isn't it dangerous?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1118
msgid ""
"But they don't work if someone is standing on the other side. I don't want to"
" know what would happen otherwise."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1124
msgid ""
"I'm afraid I have no knowledge about that. We need a volunteer to stand on "
"it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1128
msgid "Be careful. We have no idea what might happen."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1160
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/37_Old_Temple.cfg:514
msgid "Oh oh."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1189
msgid "The living quarters of the mine are behind this door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1195
msgid "Should I try to open the door?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1220
msgid "Well, it looks like they are full of orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1224
msgid "How are we supposed to get back to work if we cannot live in here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"You would do us a great favor if you could get rid of those orcs. The "
"elevator is'nt far from here so we can go down right after you are done."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1262
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1306
msgid "There is a large metal door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1357
msgid "The living quarters are cleared. Your friends can come back to mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1361
msgid ""
"Thank you Io. Here, have some gold from our reserve to help you in your "
"journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1365
msgid "Thank you Amin."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1374
msgid "Well, it looks like the elevator won't go down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1378
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1441
msgid ""
"Something must be blocking the mechanism down there. There are other "
"elevators further north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1409
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1502
msgid "I think I found an elevator."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1447
msgid "It looks like the mine continues further north. Let's go this way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1474
msgid ""
"Too many orcs and no way to go down. We will never be able to reach Hufifa "
"nor the exit of the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=14_Mine_Maze
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:4
msgid "Mine Maze"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:40
msgid "Find your way through the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:45
msgid "Defeat both orcish leaders."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:882
msgid "I don't really know the part lying further."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:886
msgid ""
"It has been abandoned a long time ago as it is full of scorpions, mine worms "
"and stone golems."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:890
msgid "I think we can add orcs to the list now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:894
msgid "Aye, I'm afraid so."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:898
msgid "Anyway, my brother is down here as is the way to Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:904
msgid "Still no sign of Hufifa or the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:908
msgid "I hope the mine doesn't go any deeper."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:912
msgid "Anyway, we don't have much other choice. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:928
msgid "It looks like there is another teleporting rune on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:947
msgid "Oh oh..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:975
msgid "It looks like the orc built a settlement here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:984
msgid ""
"If you can get rid of it, it would allow us dwarves to come back to mine this"
" area."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:990
msgid ""
"If we can get rid of it, it would allow the dwarves to come back to this "
"area."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1015
msgid "Thanks to you, us dwarves will be able to come back to mine this area."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1019
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1033
msgid "It looks like the orcs had gathered some treasures in the mines."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1023
msgid "Please take it as a mark of appreciation for helping us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1029
msgid "Now the dwarves should be able to come back to mine this area."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1037
msgid "We should leave it to the dwarves, but we also need gold for our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1041
msgid "Please take half of it and leave a message for the dwarves to apologize."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1051
msgid ""
"We have two choices here. Either we can go down that elevator or we can "
"continue north."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1053
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1526
msgid "Go down."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1066
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1539
msgid "Go north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1371
msgid "There're three barrels full of powder. Should I light them up?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1373
msgid "Yes but be careful not to get killed. The combined blast will be powerful."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1568
msgid ""
"Scorpions, ghosts, mine worms, all that on top of the orcs. We won't go "
"further with that much enemies."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=14b_Down_the_Elevator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:4
msgid "Down the Elevator"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:27
msgid "Search the level."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Stone Golem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:68
msgid "monsters"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:125
msgid "Well, it looks like we have a little welcoming comitee."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:207
msgid ""
"I think I found the other elevator. It doesn't look like this tunnel goes "
"further."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:229
msgid "Let's go back up"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14b_Down_the_Elevator.cfg:241
msgid "Wait for us. We're almost done."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=15_Ups_and_Downs
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:4
msgid "Ups and Downs"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:40
msgid "Exit the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:51
msgid "Find Hufifa before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Orcish Ruler
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:94
msgid "Orcs 1"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Orcish Ruler
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:129
msgid "Orcs 2"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:367
msgid "There we are. Back up again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:379
msgid ""
"I think I recognize this part of the mine. The elevator to the surface should"
" be north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:383
msgid ""
"We only need to find my brother and then you will be able to continue your "
"quest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:387
msgid ""
"I'm sorry Amin, but your brother is not our priority. We can try to find him,"
" but we are not even sure he is still in the mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:391
msgid "If we don't find him quickly, we will have to leave without him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:397
msgid "I have no idea where we are. And still no sign of Hufifa."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:401
msgid "But I can sense some fresh air. The exit should not be far."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:405
msgid ""
"I would like to help those dwarves, but we can't spend more time in this "
"mine."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:430
msgid "Hufifa! My Brother! We found you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:434
msgid "Aye! Well done, brother!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:440
msgid "Are you Hufifa?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:444
msgid "Of course I am! Have you heard of another dwarf kidnapped by those damn orcs?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:448
msgid "Anyway, well done!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:454
msgid ""
"Those losers weren’t really any threat, but I would bet my mine that someone "
"is pulling the strings behind them!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:458
msgid ""
"The guardian of Udxatfe must be warned, and quickly! If you go that way, I "
"would be grateful if you could warn everyone."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:462
msgid "What if he doesn't believe us?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:472
msgid "He knows me. I should be enough of a proof that our story is true."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:476
msgid "Anyway, take that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:481
msgid ""
"It's my lucky-charm. That’s the least I can do, after all you’ve done for me."
" "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:487
msgid ""
"If the guardian gives you troubles, show him my lucky-charm and he will know "
"that I’m sending you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:491
msgid "You can even keep it. Take."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:496
msgid "That’s the least I can do, after all you’ve done for me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:502
msgid "Won't you come with us?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:506
msgid ""
"I would, but I’ve got to put my guys back to work, now that you’ve cleaned "
"up. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:510
msgid ""
"Waste no time, warn the guardian of Udxatfe as quickly as possible! We will "
"cope without you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:520
msgid "Brother, go with them. They will need your help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:524
msgid "Aye, brother. Take care of the mine while I'm away."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hufifa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:528
msgid "As if I ever needed you to take care of the mine. Try not to get killed."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:784
msgid "And something is not happy about this."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:865
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1032
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1244
msgid "There's a lever to make the elevator go down. Do you want to pull it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:867
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1034
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1246
msgid "Yes, let's go down."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:943
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1017
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1086
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1155
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1229
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1303
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2932
msgid "No, not yet."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:958
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1101
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1170
msgid "There's a lever to make the elevator go up. Do you want to pull it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:960
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1103
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1172
msgid "Yes, let's go up."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1331
msgid "The elevator to the surface is behind that door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1335
msgid "Should I try to open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1362
msgid "There is a huge metal door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1381
msgid "There is an elevator behind it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1385
msgid "I see light up there. It must be the elevator to the surface."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1427
msgid "I'm sorry Amin, but we don't have the time to find your brother."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1431
msgid ""
"Well, I don't have the time to help you either! I will stay here and find my "
"brother."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1455
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall Dwarvish Fighters."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1461
msgid ""
"It is a bit sad that we did not find the dwarf, but we don't have the time to"
" search for him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1475
msgid "Hufifa is safe. We can now leave the mine without any regret."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1485
msgid ""
"My brother gave me a bit of gold that he had hidden from the orcs, to help us"
" in our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1489
msgid "That's very nice of him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1511
msgid "Wait for us! We will try to find Hufifa before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1532
msgid "We can't find Hufifa, nor the exit. We will probably die in this mine."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=16_Snow_Wizards
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:4
msgid "Snow Wizards"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:40
msgid "Reach Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:51
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders before reaching Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Troll LoI
#. [side], type=Ice Troll Warrior LoI
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:94
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:82
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:95
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:107
msgid "Ice Trolls"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Great Wolf
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:135
msgid "Wolves"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ogre
#. [side], type=Great Ogre
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:242
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:178
msgid "Ogres"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Swordsman
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:268
msgid "Guards"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:315
msgid "Finally, we are back to the surface."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:325
msgid ""
"I'm glad we found Hufifa down there. Every bit of good we can do is good to "
"take."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:335
msgid ""
"Thank you for helping me find my brother. He'd tell otherwise, but he "
"wouldn't have survived if we hadn't found him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:343
msgid ""
"I'm sad we didn't find Hufifa down there. It feels wrong leaving someone to "
"die behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:350
msgid "It looks like we arrived in a chalet in the middle of the snow."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:354
msgid ""
"That's why we don't really trade with Udxatfe. We prefer the warmth of our "
"mine to the cold of Udxatfe's weather. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:358
msgid ""
"With all this snow, we shouldn't be far from Udxatfe. It marks out the border"
" with the freezing North."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:362
msgid ""
"I don't think we will find more orcs further. I don't remember them liking "
"cold weather."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:366
msgid "Let's find Udxatfe and deliver our message."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:381
msgid ""
"West: Qyizu’s Mine. \n"
"South: Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:400
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:436
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:454
msgid "East: Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:418
msgid "North: Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Innec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:471
msgid ""
"Never had I seen wolves attacking an armed group. Something has probably made"
" them nervous."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:491
msgid "Welcome stranger."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:495
msgid ""
"The Guardian wishes to see all those coming from the south. Sorry, Legion’s "
"order."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:499
msgid "You will certainly find him at the Blessed Uaja’s Inn."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:525
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:578
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the trolls here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:548
msgid "What's this? It looks like some kind of troll. "
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:552
msgid "It's an Ice Troll."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:556
msgid ""
"They are trolls that have adapted to cold weathers. The good thing is that "
"they fear fire."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:560
msgid "It doesn't look very happy finding us on its territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:570
msgid "I'm afraid we will have to fight to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:619
msgid "We should be alright now. Those were really strange beings."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:629
msgid "So cold..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:633
msgid "Feeling numb..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/16_Snow_Wizards.cfg:637
msgid "Must not..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=17_Udxatfe
#. [side], type=Lieutenant
#. [side], type=Swordsman
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:4
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:139
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:202
msgid "Udxatfe"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:32
msgid ""
"Our hero emerged from remote lands to bring the Guardian a warning, exuding a"
" fortified spirit, ready to endure the hard tasks to come."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:72
msgid "Talk to the Guardian."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:82
msgid "Leave Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:93
msgid "Find the two remaining books."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:104
msgid "Find Roiwv, Owreddoc's sister."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Troll Hero LoI
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:379
msgid "Ice trolls"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Finally, Udaxtfe. I am glad to be there.\n"
"Now, let's find the guardian."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:435
msgid "I hate this watchtower. I could swear this old statue is watching me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:439
msgid "It is said it was already there when the first colonists arrived."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:453
msgid "Excuse me, may I ask you what you’re doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:455
msgid "Nothing"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:459
msgid "Bye then."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:474
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2632
msgid "We are looking for a book."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:478
msgid "Oh! I see, you’re reading one of those Oa’s books."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:482
msgid "Those are fine reading! I finished this one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vonin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:486
msgid ""
"I can lend it to you but don’t forget to bring it back to that mage child "
"once you’re done."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:490
msgid "Sure. We'll bring it back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Tinthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:508
msgid "You seem to have had your share of suffering, pal."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:512
msgid "We sure did."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Tinthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:516
msgid ""
"With a bit of luck, these counterattacks the guardian prepares will give me "
"something to tell my grand-children."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Cytharry
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:530
msgid "If you came to Udxatfe to shelter, you made the right choice."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Cytharry
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:534
msgid "The guardian called all the patrols up here to counterattack."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Cytharry
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Nowhere else will you see that many legionaries, except at Oof’s fortress or "
"Idaamub’s castle."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:552
msgid "It looks like you're mad at someone."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addogyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:557
msgid ""
"Damn men! My uncle’d rather listen to those morons from the legion than "
"believe his own niece!."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addogyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:562
msgid ""
"And yet, I saw Teumiuxe the mage in a dream, a prisoner in the ice caves to "
"the north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addogyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:567
msgid ""
"For generations, my whole family has had this gift, to see things in their "
"dreams."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:571
msgid "You could become a heroin with this kind of gift."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addogyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:576
msgid ""
"The problem is that for now my quest sums up to doing the cleaning and the "
"cooking. And working behind the counter, of course! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Addogyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:581
msgid "Wretched life!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugwylyn
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:595
msgid ""
"My only wish is to get back to Zei, but the guardian told me the road was "
"dangerous this week."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Innoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:609
msgid ""
"The guardian seems determined to mobilize all our military strength west of "
"Udxatfe, while captain Soimaql must fight the Dunefolk with only one troop of"
" men."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Innoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:613
msgid ""
"Soimaql is brilliant, but still! We haven't fought the Dunefolk for "
"centuries."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Innoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:617
msgid " If they are as good soldiers as smiths, the war can last."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:631
msgid ""
"Orcs have always been opportunists and will always be. Yet, I don’t "
"understand how goblins managed to excite them into their current madness."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:635
msgid "There must be another explanation behind all these inexplicable occurrences."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:639
msgid "Have you spoken to Addogyc?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:641
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:644
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:648
msgid "She says Teumiuxe the mage is prisoner in the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:655
msgid ""
"If her information are true, we are hugely indebted to her. The guardian will"
" have to replan our next move."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:659
msgid "What do you think he should do?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:663
msgid ""
"If the mage Teumiuxe is a prisoner of the goblins, we should waste no time; "
"we must leave as quickly as possible, go to the swamp in the East, and search"
" for him in their fortress."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:693
msgid "Sure, how much do you need?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:812
msgid "Excuse me. Do you happen to be the Guardian?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:840
msgid "Report the warning"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:853
msgid "Greetings. You are a long way from home."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:857
msgid ""
"Indeed. I am here to warn you that orcs attacked Zei and are roaming the land"
" around."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:861
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:879
msgid "We had to fight our way to here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:865
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:883
msgid "By the dragon, it looks like I missed a nice fight."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:869
msgid "Men have died!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:875
msgid ""
"We come in behalf of Csia of Zei to warn you that orcs attacked the city and "
"are roaming the land around."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:887
msgid "Well... that's one way to see it..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:893
msgid ""
"Ha! The legionaries are saying it is even worse on the other side of the "
"mountain."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:897
msgid ""
"Dunefolk mounted archers are pillaging villages east and I heard orcish "
"marauders are looking for some kind of magic artifact…"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:908
msgid "Find out what is happening"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:912
msgid "Excuse me, what is happening here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:916
msgid ""
"Everything began the day our great mage Teumiuxe disappeared and if you want "
"my opinion, it’s not a coincidence!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:920
msgid ""
"That mad innkeeper says she knows where he is, but I tell you he is dead or "
"kept as a hostage at our little friend's from East."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:931
msgid "Propose your help"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:941
msgid "Can we do something to help?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:945
msgid "You seems like capable people."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:949
msgid "I need someone to go east and find Teumiuxe, dead or alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:953
msgid "Find him and you’ll find at the same time the reason for this mess!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1005
msgid "Me Uwiu. Strong warrior."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1020
msgid "Chief tell Uwiu bring caravan Idaamub’s kingdom."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1024
msgid "Uwiu bring Zei and stupid orcs burn city!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1028
msgid "Driver steal wagon, steal gold Uwiu and flee."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1032
msgid "Uwiu follow to Udxatfe but can’t go further."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1043
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1251
msgid "We are looking for some strong recruit for our group. Are you interested?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1051
msgid "Uwiu help you if you help him. Uwiu need 1700 gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1055
msgid "Uwiu good to strike, hit, break…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1059
msgid "Everything and everyone!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1063
msgid "You OK?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1065
msgid "We OK."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1075
msgid "Not enough gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1079
msgid "Uwiu need gold or no go back home."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1100
msgid "Ah-ah! You make perfect choice! Excellent!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1104
msgid "We have fun a lot hit orcs, save kingdom!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1108
msgid "You can now recruit thugs."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1115
msgid "Sorry, we not enough gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1119
msgid "You think about that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1123
msgid "Uwiu wait, stay here for when you want strong warrior, OK?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1127
msgid "Well. well. See you later."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1179
msgid "I'm Asaem, a mage."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1183
msgid ""
"I’m the best mage around. I might be a bit decrepit, but my fireballs were "
"already grilling goblins when your grandfather was still wearing diapers."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1198
msgid "I was in a quest with other adventurers, but it went poorly."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1202
msgid "<span font='italic'>Starts singing</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1206
msgid ""
"In this inn where we met, I bumped into 5 to 6 soldiers. At least 4 wanted to"
" hit me. Instead they trampled my black cat."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1210
msgid ""
"If I had known this spell, it never would have happened. If I had known this "
"spell, unfortunately I had forgotten it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1214
msgid ""
"We arrived at the dungeon door, I wanted to try to lockpick it. Then a trap "
"triggered, and the rogue got killed."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1218
msgid ""
"If I had had my scroll, I could have detected it. If I had had my scroll, but"
" it was covered all over with wine stains."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1222
msgid ""
"In the first corridor we were exploring, a herd of orcs arrived. I cast a "
"fireball at them. But the dwarf received it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1226
msgid ""
"If I had had this old book, I would probably have aimed better. If I had had "
"this old book, the one I lost the evening before."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1230
msgid ""
"In the cellar that we escaped, we thought we were safe. Then we ran into a "
"troll, of course the elf got eaten."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1234
msgid ""
"If I had grabbed my wand, I could have petrified it. If I had grabbed my "
"wand. I did not because it was in pieces."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1238
msgid ""
"In the catacombs we were hiding in, I brushed against a huge bell. The dragon"
" I awoke used the warrior as his breakfast."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1242
msgid ""
"If I had had the One Ring, I would have crushed this dragon. If I had had the"
" One Ring that was stolen one day from me by a hobbit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1246
msgid "I am not sure if he is unsafe or just mad as a hatter."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1265
msgid ""
"If the Guardian decided to give you an impossible quest, I need to give you "
"at least a chance to stay alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1271
msgid "I just need 1950 gold to pay my bill at the inn."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"If you have enough to pay my bill, we can go before you can say Jack "
"Robinson."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1279
msgid "It's up to you."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1281
msgid "Here is the gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1291
msgid "I'm sorry, but there is not enough to pay my bill"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1312
msgid "Well. Then, let’s go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1316
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:739
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1151
msgid "You can now recruit mages."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1323
msgid "Sorry, we don't have that much gold to spend."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1327
msgid "You’re quite reckless but do as you feel."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1331
msgid "I’ll be there when you’ll be back to your mind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1361
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1379
msgid "Excuse me, do you know what is happening here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aethyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1365
msgid ""
"From what I heard, the Guardian requisitioned the patrols on duty along Oa’s "
"gallery to have enough men to ensure the protection of Qyizu and Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vobreorer
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1383
msgid "It is said the mystical seal of the queen’s men was seen here last week. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vobreorer
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1391
msgid "I asked the captain about that, and he extended my patrol by one week."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vobreorer
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1395
msgid "But I still don’t know why everyone make such a mystery about this!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhyrthynaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1410
msgid ""
"I’m sorry but we are not used to see so many legionaries on leave at the same"
" time. Can you please stay here until a room is free?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Alyn
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1414
msgid ""
"If the Guardian hadn’t called me back on his duty, I could sleep quietly in "
"my bed instead of in this bloody corridor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugthynyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1428
msgid "It’s quite cold, isn’t it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugthynyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1432
msgid ""
"Gods be blessed, I don’t have to live here year long. I only come to do some "
"experiments."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugthynyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1436
msgid "Fire and ice spells, that kind of things."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugthynyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1440
msgid ""
"You see, I’ve a theory about that: if the spells work fine here, it should be"
" the same anywhere else. Udxatfe has always been a special place where magic "
"holds an important place! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Vugthynyr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1444
msgid "Probably because of the magic ice cave in the North."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1494
msgid "You can look at my potions and spells if you’re interested."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1546
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:5421
msgid "A Dynamical Theory of the Electromagnetic Field"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1574
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1185
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1574
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1888
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1824
msgid "Experience potion"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1575
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1186
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1575
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1889
msgid "Healing potion"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1576
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1187
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1576
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1825
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6042
msgid "Small potion of rejuvenation"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1631
msgid "Excuse me"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teddthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1635
msgid "Can't you see I'm busy?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teddthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1639
msgid ""
"Someone troubled the spirit of the dead last week and now I need to provide "
"them with fresh supplies."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teddthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1643
msgid ""
"If you need something, ask Vugthynyr. He is the one selling to the living "
"this week."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1663
msgid "You seem worried. Can we help you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1667
msgid "Master Vugthynyr gonna kill me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1671
msgid ""
"I borrowed a trilogy of books about Oa’s gallery and gave them to two "
"friends, but I forgot whom!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1675
msgid ""
"Vugthynyr has forbidden me from leaving when he’s keeping the shop, but "
"there’s no doubt he's gonna find out,… He'll find out any moment, that "
"they’re gone."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1679
msgid "Could you please use a few minutes and enquire in town?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1681
msgid "Sure, we'll find them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1685
msgid "It’s very kind of you, stranger. I will gladly make up for the trouble."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1689
msgid "Here is one of the books, so you know exactly how they look."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1694
msgid "You receive an old book called ``Oa's gallery, volume 3''."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1701
msgid "Sorry, we don't have the time for that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1705
msgid "A-are you sure? Oh my! He really is gonna kill me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1729
msgid "Thousand thanks, pal.  You allowed me to keep my job, and maybe my life."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1733
msgid "Accept this gold, this food and all my gratitude for your help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teoran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1747
msgid "Remember, I need the three books."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1767
msgid ""
"South: Zei, Qyizu’s mine\n"
"North-east: Alpine caves, Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreoryr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1785
msgid "It’s been at least twenty years since we have last seen ogres around here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Marthynec
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1799
msgid ""
"I swear on the welkin that I saw an ogre on my way from my guardhouse in the "
"caves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gorcyn
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1813
msgid ""
"Sarearan is the best blacksmith in the region. I’m glad he had the time to "
"repair my armor with all those reservists of the Legion in town."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1827
msgid ""
"I needed this job at the blacksmith to pay for my room at the Blessed Uaja’s "
"Inn ; my basement has become the lair of enormous frost monsters, and each "
"time I opened the door of my house, a group of wolves swooped down on me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1831
msgid ""
"I don’t know when I’ll be able to go back, but Saraeran needs help and "
"proposed to lend me his adventurer’s stuff if I keep working well during the "
"Legion's demobilization."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1835
msgid "Maybe we can help you with that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1840
msgid "Well, you look determined."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1844
msgid ""
"You will find in the basement a chest and some crates. If you successfully "
"get rid of the monsters prowling around, you can take what you want."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1848
msgid ""
"My house is in the woods, north-west of Udxatfe. I am afraid the path will be"
" full of snow as I am not there to clean it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1862
msgid "Ah, young people, they all believe they will be able to save the world. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1866
msgid ""
"I had the same light in the eyes, before. I was not the last one to look for "
"a fight, but I ended up by hanging my sword back up."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1870
msgid ""
"I can’t say this work is hard but well, you don’t see many people… Except for"
" some time. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1874
msgid "Something bad is brewing. I feel it…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1884
msgid "So, by the way, you’re leaving for the ice caves?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Seraeran
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1888
msgid ""
"One must be wary of the slippery slopes. I advise you to equip yourselves for"
" cold and climbing."
msgstr ""

