msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2457
msgid "Intact turtle shield"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2494
msgid "Excuse me. Are you by any chance Owreddoc's sister?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2499
msgid "Yes, I am. How do you know her?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2503
msgid "We come from Zei. The city was attacked."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2507
msgid "Your house was destroyed but your sister is fine. She asked us to tell you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2512
msgid ""
"Thank you for that information all in all mixed: my sister is alive, but our "
"house is nearly destroyed."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2517
msgid ""
"I thank you strangers anyway for bringing me news of my sister. How could I "
"show you my gratitude?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2522
msgid "Hmmmm..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2527
msgid ""
"My father got this ring as a gift after saving the life of a group of "
"minstrels who had fallen into a troll's ambush. It might be time someone "
"worthy wore it; I myself, did nothing to deserve this honor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2532
msgid ""
"I only ask that you to give it to some brave person’s care once you have no "
"more use of it; in memory of my father."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2538
msgid "Here is also some food for your journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Roiwr
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2547
msgid "May luck travel with you in your journey"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Siraery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2561
msgid "A new face. You must be the man who successfully came here from Zei."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2565
msgid "Well, yes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Siraery
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2569
msgid ""
"I hope you don’t wish to go further than Udxatfe, otherwise your road might "
"be difficult after the eastern swamp, given we drew back the troops."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Mulyn
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2583
msgid ""
"I imagine it must not be too hard to be stationed here. Better stay half a "
"day in the cold than pace up and down the Green Mountains looking for "
"bandits."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2597
msgid ""
"Still another day of severe cold in the mountains. As soon as my wife has "
"sold all those stupid pack mules, we will move to settle somewhere warm."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2611
msgid "Eh, where do you think you are? Shut the door tightly!"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2613
msgid "Sorry, we had no intention of disturbing you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2617
msgid "Then leave! And shut the door tightly!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2636
msgid "Oh, you’re looking for books? To tell the truth, Teoran just lent me one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2640
msgid "He needs it back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Gwatharvan
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2644
msgid "No problem. Here it is. You can thank him for me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2648
msgid "Sure. We'll bring him back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2666
msgid "I suppose you came to buy me a mule?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2670
msgid "Well not"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2674
msgid "Don’t say anything, I know… "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2678
msgid ""
"You need a docile animal, that can carry heavy burdens, that can travel in "
"the rain, and you can feed when you think about it? That’s it, isn’t it? Of "
"course, but yacks don’t sell!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2699
msgid "I can sell you one for the modest price of 1750 gold."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2701
msgid "I'm sorry but we don't need a mule."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2705
msgid ""
"Do me a favor: buy one of those worthless mules so I can leave this bloody "
"kingdom once and for all."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2711
msgid "Well, I have to say that mules are really practical."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2725
msgid "Of course they are. But I won't give it to you for free."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2744
msgid "I wonder how pratical a yack would be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Derrreddoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2748
msgid "Unless you like yack butter tea, I don't think you'll like them. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Meoddaent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2771
msgid "Sorry, this sector is forbidden to civilians. Let me mount the guardpost."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2791
msgid ""
"My friends, our new mission is to find Teumiuxe the mage. We were told he is "
"a prisoner in the ice caves in the North."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2795
msgid ""
"*To himself* I hope he is alive. He might know what is happening, and we will"
" need him to save Idaamub. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2823
msgid ""
"It looks like someone build that wall later than the others. I think I could "
"take it down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2827
msgid "Should I try?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2842
msgid "Well, it was easier than I expected."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:2847
msgid "No. This wall was surely built for a good reason."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=18_In_the_Snow
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:4
msgid "In the Snow"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:26
msgid "Go north"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:31
msgid "Find the path to Ery's house"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:247
msgid "My friends, a new adventure awaits us. A cold one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:251
msgid ""
"From what we have heard, the ice cave should be north of here. They are "
"supposed to be full of dangers."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, this is where we are going. The great mage Teumiuxe is "
"supposedly prisoner in there and we need to free him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:259
msgid ""
"He should have information on what is happening and his great magic should "
"help us end the troubles."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:269
msgid ""
"We should also pass in front Ery's house. He asked us to clean his basement "
"from frost monsters."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:273
msgid "We'll see if we have the time for that we'll be there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:295
msgid "There is a path here. It seems to lead to a house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:305
msgid "It must be Ery's house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:311
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:324
msgid "Wait for us"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:348
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/20_Ice_Cave.cfg:968
msgid "Let's continue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:362
msgid "Wait for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Runin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:380
msgid "Snow is tricking me, but I’d swear I have seen things moving around today. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Runin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:384
msgid ""
"If I were you, I’d go back to the inn and eat a good stew ‘til the end of the"
" storm."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:398
msgid "You chose the wrong week to go north.  "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:402
msgid ""
"The road won’t be passable before several month, and the Guardian withdrew "
"all the legionary patrols that were in duty in the underground caves during "
"the attacks. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:406
msgid ""
"There’s no doubt the trolls will have a field day while we’re away. Good luck"
" if you go there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Voboger
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:410
msgid "May Of bless you, pal."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:418
msgid "It was the wrong week to go north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:422
msgid "We should have stayed in the inn with a good stew."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18_In_the_Snow.cfg:426
msgid "Now they will only find our frozen corpses in several months."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:42
msgid "Find the road to the ice caves"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:53
msgid "Clean the cave"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Ice Crab
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:183
msgid "Frost Monsters"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:270
msgid "Ery's house should be a bit more north. Let's try to find it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:274
msgid ""
"Once we will have cleaned his cave, we will need to find the road back "
"though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:280
msgid "Well, there doesn't seem to be a clear path that way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:284
msgid ""
"It might have been a better idea to stay to the right. But I'm sure we will "
"find the path back soon."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:288
msgid "There is only one way to find out anyway. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:319
msgid "I found Ery's house!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:325
msgid "There's a house here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:329
msgid "I wonder who can live there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:356
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:575
msgid "Could this be an Ice Golem?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:360
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:579
msgid ""
"Considering where we are, I think they could have spawned naturally from the "
"ambient ice magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:364
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:583
msgid ""
"Or they could have been summoned by the Ice Troll Shamans. I hope the first "
"option is the right one though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:370
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:589
msgid "What are those thing?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:380
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:599
msgid "I think they are Ice Golems."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:384
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:603
msgid ""
"Considering where we are, I think they might have spawned naturally from the "
"ambient ice magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:388
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:607
msgid ""
"Or they could have been summoned by the Ice Troll Shamans. I hope the first "
"option is the right one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:413
msgid "There's a chest on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:417
msgid "It looks like it was dragged from the north."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:421
msgid "It's locked."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:432
msgid "The key opened the chest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:438
msgid "Let's see what's inside."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:456
msgid "There's a key on the floor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:460
msgid "Let's take it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:476
msgid "Brrrr. It's cold in here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:503
msgid ""
"The cave is clean. Now let's continue to the ice caves. The road should be "
"east from the house."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:513
msgid "Let's take a look at the chest before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:523
msgid "Look what we have here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:555
msgid "I found the road."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:559
msgid "Let's go then."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/18b_Frozen_Cave.cfg:572
msgid "This is pointless! Let's go back to the road where we left it."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=19_Frozen_Maze
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Maze"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:45
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:32
msgid "Defeat the troll leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:55
msgid "Continue north"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:535
msgid "I think I heard noises coming from the East."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:539
msgid "Be prepared. I think we are entering to the core of the ice trolls territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:543
msgid "We will probably need to defeat them if we want to continue our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:629
msgid "It's getting foggy out there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:633
msgid "I think I can see a path though."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:637
msgid "Wait! I see two!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:641
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:369
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:465
msgid "Which way should we go?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:643
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:371
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:467
msgid "North"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:647
msgid "Let's go North. That should be the way to the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:659
msgid "East"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:663
msgid "Let's go East. That should be the way to the ice caves."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:675
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:431
msgid "Not now"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:679
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:435
msgid "Let's decide later. We are not done here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:696
msgid "It should be easier now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:700
msgid ""
"I don't say that we won't cross the path of some more trolls, but at least "
"the leader is dead."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:708
msgid "So...cold..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/19_Frozen_Maze.cfg:712
msgid "Can't...think..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=19b_Northern_Lights
