#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1156
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8119
msgid "Bringing back the soul"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1157
msgid "Stingy tail"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1158
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7393
msgid "Animating skeletons"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1357
msgid "I won't sell you food for it to get wasted."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1402
msgid "I know this cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"It is full of trolls and saurians. They will not be very happy to see us on "
"their territory. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1410
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, this is the shortest way to the eastern swamp, and this is "
"were my staff seems to be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1416
msgid ""
"I don't like the look of this cave. I'm sure it is full of deadly creatures, "
"lurking in the dark.  "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1420
msgid "Unfortunately, it seems to be the only way to continue our travel."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1424
msgid "We need to reach the eastern swamp and recover Teumiuxe's staff."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=24_Deep_Water
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:4
msgid "Deep Water"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:25
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:27
msgid "Cross the cave"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:36
msgid "Stop the agressive fishes before leaving"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Sea Serpent
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:81
msgid "Fishes"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Saurian Ambusher
#. [side], type=Water Serpent
#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:99
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:96
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:92
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:75
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:159
msgid "Saurians"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:355
msgid ""
"I didn't expect so much water in this cave. I can see it streaming down the "
"walls and I can hear droplets falling on the ground."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:359
msgid "This cave is really special you know."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:363
msgid ""
"It was formed a long time ago, when an spell went entropic made an underwater"
" cave rise above the ground."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:367
msgid "Since then, the cave still contain water, but also a lot of magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:371
msgid "It is even said that you can meet sea creatures in it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:375
msgid "Alright everyone! Try not to slip."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:379
msgid ""
"The exit should be south. But we will probably have to fight the saurians for"
" that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:398
msgid "I know there is a lot of water here, but I did not expect to see a fish."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:403
msgid ""
"They seem agressive. I am afraid we will have to fight them on top of the "
"saurians."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:416
msgid ""
"This horror was probably the mother of the fishes. We should have some peace "
"now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:436
msgid ""
"Crossing this cave is difficult enough with all those saurians, and now we "
"had to fight fishes on top of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:440
msgid ""
"I don't know how long this cave is, but I hope the situation will be better "
"on the other side of it. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:444
msgid "Unfortunately, with what we heard in Udxatfe, I am afraid it won't be."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:477
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the fishes here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:485
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the saurians here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:497
msgid ""
"I don't think we will be able to pass through both the saurians and the "
"fishes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/24_Deep_Water.cfg:501
msgid "We need to find another way."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=25_Troll_Cave
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Cave"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Bay Horse
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:421
msgid "Horse"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:503
msgid "Wait! I recognize this noise."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:507
msgid ""
"It sounds exactly like the ice troll leader we defeated before entering the "
"ice cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:511
msgid "But it should be too warm here for the ice trolls?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:515
msgid ""
"You are unfortunately right. This cave is full of trolls. Not the ice "
"version, but the normal ones."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:519
msgid ""
"When I withdrew all the legionary patrols that were in duty in the "
"underground caves during the attacks, there’s no doubt the trolls had a field"
" day while they were away."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:523
msgid ""
"We need to kill the troll leader. That should disorganize them enough that we"
" can easily take back control of the cave later."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:527
msgid "I am afraid we will have to fight those trolls to continue our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:542
msgid ""
"South: Black Forest\n"
"North: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:566
msgid ""
"I do not like leaving those trolls roaming the path behind us, but we have a "
"more important mission than dealing with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:593
msgid ""
"Now that we dealt with those trolls, the traffic should be able to start "
"again from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:597
msgid "Let's try to find the exit of this cave... and the staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:611
msgid "First saurians, then fishes and now trolls."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:615
msgid "That's too much for us. We are not legionaries."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:628
msgid "Hey there, pal. Don't worry, you're safe now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:632
msgid "That's quite a bad situation you got into. Want to come with us?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:662
msgid "There's a horse here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:666
msgid "What is it doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:670
msgid "Maybe it fled from fear and got stuck here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/25_Troll_Cave.cfg:674
msgid "It will not leave long alone here. Maybe we could try to get to it."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=26_Echo_Chamber
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:4
msgid "Echo Chamber"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat enemy leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:29
msgid "Defeat all enemies"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:322
msgid ""
"It sounds like there are more trolls ahead. They must be in a huge room by "
"the echo."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:326
msgid "Anyway, we need to advance. I am sure the exit is not far."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:338
msgid "Oh, I understand the echo now. The chamber is not huge, it is really deep."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:351
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:461
msgid "The road splits here. We can go north or south."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:362
msgid ""
"The road north leads to the legionaries fort. It is a dead end but I am "
"afraid it is now full of trolls. \n"
"The road south continue to the exit of the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:381
msgid "We should clean the fort before leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:387
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:471
msgid "Let's go North. That should be the way out."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:401
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:483
msgid "South"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:411
msgid "We have no time to clean the fort. Our mission is too urgent."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:417
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:487
msgid "Let's go South. That should be the way out."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:455
msgid "It is so quiet now. I think this was the last one."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=26b_Troll_Fort
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Fort"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:50
msgid "Clean the fort"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:268
msgid "Those ruins looks weird. They don't look like something trolls would build."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:278
msgid ""
"They are indeed no troll ruins. This is where the legionary patrols were "
"living in the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:282
msgid ""
"The fort is a bit north.\n"
"It would be good to flush them out of it. Legionaries would then have an "
"easier time coming here to patrol again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:289
msgid ""
"There seems to be some kind of fort further north. I imagine the path goes "
"through it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:453
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:684
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:791
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1026
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1133
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1612
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1704
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it down?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:478
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:701
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:816
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1043
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1158
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1664
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1733
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it up?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1203
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1270
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1337
msgid "There is a chest. Should I open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1217
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1284
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1351
msgid "It is empty."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1233
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1300
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1367
msgid "Argh! The chest was trapped."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1241
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1308
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1375
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:442
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:459
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:476
msgid "There is something in the chest."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1248
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1315
msgid "No, it might be trapped."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1417
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. We can go back to the crossing and"
" take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1445
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. We do not have enough time to clean the "
"whole fort.\n"
"                                                        Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1458
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1492
msgid ""
"We already spent too much time here. I don't think the exit is this way.\n"
"                                                        Let's go back to the "
"crossing and take the other road."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1479
msgid ""
"I think there are no more trolls in there. \n"
"                                                        Let's go back to the "
"crossing and take the other path to the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=27_Saurian_Pond
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Pond"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat the saurian leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:31
msgid "Defeat all leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Purple Crystal LoI
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:162
msgid "Crystals"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:297
msgid ""
"I am a bit worried about letting those trolls behind us. I hope they will not"
" come to stab us in the back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:307
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we don't have time to worry now. We are now entering the saurian "
"territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:311
msgid "They might not be as impressive as trolls, but they are fierce warriors."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:317
msgid ""
"We do not have time to worry though. We must find the exit of this cave and "
"the protection staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:326
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:341
msgid "It should be a bit better now that we have killed the troll leaders."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:330
msgid ""
"I'm however afraid that we might only have killed some of them. There might "
"still be more hidden in the cave we left."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:334
msgid ""
"However, I do not think this is a good time to think about that. Even if we "
"had killed all trolls in this cave, there are still others enemies awaiting "
"us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:345
msgid "This is unfortunately not how it works."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:349
msgid ""
"There is now an empty spot in the hierarchy of the cave. The other creatures "
"are going to fight to find out which will take their place."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:353
msgid "Be prepared to fight aggressive creatures."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:357
msgid "Wait, you mean we should have left the trolls live."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:361
msgid ""
"No, we had to deal with them. But now we need to deal with the other "
"creatures. Otherwise the cave will be even more dangerous in the following "
"weeks, the time needed for things to calm down."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:380
msgid "That's one huge crystal."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:384
msgid ""
"It looks like it is controlling the other ones. Maybe destroying it would "
"disturb the others for a while."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:403
msgid "That was a hard fight, but I think we cleaned the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:407
msgid "It even looks like this one was guardian a treasure."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:411
msgid ""
"Not that we are doing that for gold, but we might need it for our journey. "
"Take it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:415
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:445
msgid ""
"I'm glad we finally found the exit. I would not have spent another day in "
"that cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:441
msgid ""
"It is a mess here with all those creatures fighting for their small part of "
"this cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Let's leave before they decide that we are more interesting than protecting "
"their territory."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:461
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:555
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:595
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:656
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1682
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:474
msgid ""
"There are too many creatures there. Let's go back and try to find another way"
" through the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/27_Saurian_Pond.cfg:491
msgid ""
"North-West: Black Forest\n"
"South-East: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=28_Travelers
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:4
msgid "Travelers"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:38
msgid "Find the camp fire."
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:48
msgid "Leave south."
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Duelist
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:296
msgid "Travellers"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:403
msgid "Finally back outside. I was getting tired of the trolls."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Well, now that you mention it, the legion was not only controlling the trolls"
" INSIDE the cave. It was also preventing them from going OUTSIDE the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:417
msgid ""
"So what you are telling me is that we should expect more trolls out here, "
"shouldn't we?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:421
msgid "I'm afraid so."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:425
msgid "What did I do to deserve this?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:431
msgid "I'm sorry to be a bummer, but it looks lie there are trolls outside too."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:435
msgid "Oh, come on!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:441
msgid "Wait, don't you smell smoke?"
msgstr ""

#. [1]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:445
msgid "Could be a distress fire... or a barbecue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:449
msgid "A distress barbecue?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Anyway, we need to find out if it comes from friends or foes, if it is a good"
" or a bad news."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:457
msgid "I sure hope it's a barbecue."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:471
msgid "Who goez there? Friend or foe?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:475
msgid "I don't know, who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:479
msgid ""
"What do you mean you don't know? Are you ztupid or are you trying to get "
"killed?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:483
msgid "We are travellerz? What about you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:487
msgid ""
"We are a party on a mission for the kingdom of Idaamub. But it is a secret "
"mission."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:491
msgid "Then you're friendz. You might actually even be able to help uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:495
msgid ""
"You can get zome rezt in our camp. We could even do some buzinezz if you have"
" zome money or thingz to zell."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:499
msgid "We smelled the smoke of your fire from far away. Was it a distress signal?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:503
msgid "No, we're juzt grilling some meat."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:507
msgid "I knew it!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:511
msgid ""
"Well, it looks like we found the source of the smell. They don't seem to be "
"in immediate trouble, so I think we can continue as soon as we want."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:539
msgid ""
"My friends, It seems our mission is getting more dangerous. From what we "
"learnt here, we won't have to face only the goblins to get the staff back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:543
msgid "Anyway, this cannot stop us, as the destiny of Idaamub is in our hands."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:565
msgid "Wait a minute. We still need to find where this smell comes from."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:582
msgid "It muzt have been written zomewhere that our life will only be zuffering."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:590
msgid ""
"The men of our camp are buzy anzwering the bravado of the harmlezz bandits, "
"but I zee emerging a danger far greater than those banditz. Be careful if you"
" go in the zwamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:594
msgid "What is the problem?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Rhadoc
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:598
msgid ""
"During more than a month, my zizterz and I had nightmarez in which we were "
"zeeing an huge army of zoullezz goblinz. There were bowing down before a huge"
" black zymbol of power which waz getting bigger and bigger, fulled by the "
"revenge and the hatred of the abyzz’ demonz. I fear the powerluzt of the "
"goblins cauzez an invazion of the forcez of evil."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ritharry
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:612
msgid ""
"We are indeed going through a trial. It began with the rapt of our zizter "
"Bta, and now the banditz are threatening to kill uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:626
msgid "Evil-eyed creaturez… came… and took my Bta."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:630
msgid "What kind of creatures?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:634
msgid ""
"They look like the horrible Ockz from the legendz… but how could it be "
"pozzible? The Ockz were killed… slaughtered three hundred yearz ago by the "
"first king of your kingdom. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fdi
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:638
msgid ""
"But I am confident my daughter will give them a hard time. She is a… "
"Traveler."
msgstr ""

