#. [message], speaker=Celyn
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1290
msgid ""
"It iz true the banditz are uzing uz to their endz, but they never attacked "
"uz. \n"
"We are Travellerz, not barbarianz. \n"
"We try not to provoke them, and they don’t dare taking it out on uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hury
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1306
msgid ""
"Fdi is zo afflicted by the lozz of Bta that he iz not aware of the growing "
"threat that are banditz and goblinz eazt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1310
msgid "How are they a threat?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Hury
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1314
msgid ""
"We gave them too much and they want more. \n"
"If only we still had Bta and Ubidaiubua with uz, we could probably defend "
"ourzelvez, but without them, we gonna get zlaughtered."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1329
msgid ""
"It is zaid that a hero is fazing the danger of Oa’z gallery despite the "
"legion’z withdrawal. Could it be you, that grandee? "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1333
msgid "Yes, this should be us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1337
msgid ""
"In that case, the Black Zizter azked me to tell you about the danger that iz "
"threatening uz, but you muzt promise me not the tell a word to the women from"
" our camp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1341
msgid "Who is the Black Sister?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1345
msgid "This is not relevant."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1349
msgid ""
"In the pazt, the banditz were tolerating uz because we were zupplying them "
"but zince the legion withdrawn its troopz, the banditz who were committing "
"petty theftz and robbing caravanz are now pillaging and killing."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1353
msgid "This sounds quite bad."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1357
msgid ""
"This morning, we found one buzy ztealing in Koezaran’s tent. He told uz that "
"the bandit leader claim the property of the women and goodz of our camp and "
"that they will come back tonight in force to help themzelvez."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1361
msgid "Can't you do anything to prevent that?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1365
msgid ""
"This makez me zick. The Green Mountainz are right behind uz, but we cannot "
"face Oa’s gallery without Bta’s and Ubidaiubua’s help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1369
msgid "I see. There are the bandits in front and the dangers of the gallery behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1377
msgid ""
"If you’re a true hero, you muzt be courageouz enough to fight the bandit "
"leader for uz."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1381
msgid "But wha"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1385
msgid ""
"You won’t get any reward in return, but I would bet he amazzed a zmall "
"fortune in his bandit’z lair."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1389
msgid "So whe"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Ve
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1393
msgid "You muzt zwear to ztay zilent until your clash with the bandit leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Evuyjixcih
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1407
msgid ""
"I’ll go straight to the point, my child, as I’m old and some things can’t "
"wait anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1411
msgid "Tell us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Evuyjixcih
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1415
msgid "Your kingdom is dancing with evil forces."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1419
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter6/39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:168
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Evuyjixcih
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1423
msgid ""
"The current events are the harvest of what the irresponsible have sown a long"
" time ago. They touched what should have been left in peace. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1427
msgid "Not helping?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Evuyjixcih
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1431
msgid "You will need a lot of allies, but you first must save your kingdom."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1482
msgid "If you need potions or magic items, they are yours at low price."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1542
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9400
msgid "A soul black as night"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1543
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9418
msgid "Regeneration"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1544
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9434
msgid "Ice breath"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1545
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9540
msgid "Focused spirit"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1546
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9555
msgid "To make a corpse explode"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1573
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1887
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8839
msgid "Potion of rejuvenation"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1786
msgid "I'm Eukhac, the best bowwoman of Idaamub."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1801
msgid "I am ruined, fully ruined!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1805
msgid ""
"During six years, all my money and all my efforts went into the preparation "
"of the contest of best bowman of the known lands. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1809
msgid ""
"But the day right before the contest, catastrophe! Our funds were stolen by "
"the goblins! Our prizes were stolen! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1813
msgid "I only have my bow and my talent left to try to save my stained reputation."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1817
msgid ""
"I followed the goblins down to here, but I can’t go any further as I ain’t "
"got a dime to buy food. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1836
msgid ""
"If you have a bit of gold for me, I would be glad to help you. That way, I "
"would continue looking for my stolen treasure in good company."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1840
msgid "I would need 38400 gold to reimburse the Travellers and buy some food."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1844
msgid "Can you help me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1856
msgid "I am afraid you don't have enough gold to help me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1900
msgid ""
"The bow and honor of Eukhac are yours, my good friend. I am glad to follow "
"you."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1913
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1161
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:853
msgid "Sorry, we don't have enough gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1917
msgid "Please excuse me for my straightforward request. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1921
msgid "I should have seen that your funds are in the same state as mines."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1925
msgid "Farewell, then, and may luck be in your favor."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=29_Black_Forest
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:4
msgid "Black Forest"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:34
msgid "Cross the Black Forest to the Eastern Swamp"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:39
msgid "Also kill all remaining trolls"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Bandit
#. [side], type=Huntsman
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:344
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:97
msgid "Bandits"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:435
msgid "This forest is quite dark."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:439
msgid "This is the Black Forest. As you realized, it is well named."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:443
msgid ""
"Well, it seems we have to cross it to reach the Eastern Swamp and find "
"Teumiuxe's staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:447
msgid "Please, everyone, be careful and don't get lost in the woods."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:464
msgid ""
"I saw something moving in the woods. It looks like some kind of huge boar "
"with glowing red eyes."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:468
msgid "It must be a Hell Boar."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:472
msgid ""
"It is said they were bread by the Ocks to be used as yoke for their wagons. "
"When they disappeared, they went free and established in the Black Forest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Be careful everyone. Remember that boars are omnivorous, which means it could"
" try to use you as a snack."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:494
msgid "There is a huge troll here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:498
msgid ""
"This must be what's left of the vanguard. If we deal with them, we will be "
"done with the trolls that escaped the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:516
msgid "South: Eastern Swamp"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:536
msgid "That's it. It must've been the last one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:540
msgid ""
"This is a good thing. Trolls are already a pain in the cave, we don't want "
"them outside of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:561
msgid "I can see the bandits' camp from here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:565
msgid "Everyone, be quiet. We will try to pass without them spotting us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:582
msgid ""
"At least we dealt with the trolls before fighting the bandits. We don't want "
"to fear being attacked from behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:609
msgid "Wheeee!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:613
msgid "Aaahhh!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/29_Black_Forest.cfg:617
msgid "You were eaten by a Hell Boar."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=30_Bandit_Camp
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:4
msgid "Bandit Camp"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:48
msgid "Avoid the bandits to continue west"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:53
msgid "Defeat the bandit leader"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:400
msgid "Alas."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:407
msgid "They spotted us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:411
msgid ""
"This looks like a forward camp. It must be there for this exact purpose: "
"spotting travellers and calling troops to capture or kill them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:415
msgid "I don't think we can pass undetected now..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:419
msgid "But we can still try to get across faster than their troops arrive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:423
msgid "Or we try to help the Travelers and we fight them and defeat their leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:488
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:521
msgid "That's it! We defeated the bandit leader!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=insecond
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:496
msgid "In your dream..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=insecond
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:500
msgid "I was only a decay. You will never find our leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:506
msgid "I am afraid he was only the second-in-command."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:510
msgid "The true leader must be hiding somewhere."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:539
msgid "Let's have a look at the chests before leaving"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:555
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:577
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:599
msgid "There was something in the chest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:611
msgid "It looks like they had gathered quite a treasure."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Now, let's continue to the Eastern Swamp. We need to find Teumiuxe's staff "
"before something worse happens."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:640
msgid ""
"I'm a bit sorry that we are leaving the Travelers at the mercy of the "
"bandits, but we have to find Teumiuxe's staff as soon as possible."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:644
msgid "Let's continue to the Eastern Swamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:668
msgid "Bandits... there are too many of them..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/30_Bandit_Camp.cfg:672
msgid "We would need an army to be able to cross."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:25
msgid "Haaa! There was a huge serpent hidden in the mud."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=31_Corrupted_Temple
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:34
msgid "Corrupted Temple"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:64
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:35
msgid "Find the goblin's lair"
msgstr ""

#. [objective], condition=win
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:69
msgid "Purify the temple"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=Necromancer
#. [side], type=Dark Sorcerer
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1122
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:97
msgid "Witches"
msgstr ""

#. [side], type=White Mage
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1273
msgid "Ofites"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1354
msgid "What's that smell?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1358
msgid "THE SWAMP! IT'S THE SWAMP! WE'RE FINALLY THERE!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1362
msgid "I thought we never gonna get out of this dark forest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1366
msgid "Now, we need to find where the goblin's hiding. I wonder how hard it can be."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1374
msgid ""
"Well, I never heard about a goblin living in this swamp. So he's either "
"hiding well or don't actually live there. Let's hope for the first one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1378
msgid "Is it more bandits I see here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1382
msgid ""
"Yes but it's nothing to worry about. It's most probably their second forward "
"camp, on the other side of the forest. There shouldn't be too many bandits "
"there, and they won't follow us into the swamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1402
msgid ""
"South: Salvage Trading Post\n"
"North-east : Black Forest"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1427
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:2024
msgid "The tree. It's attacking me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1431
msgid "It is no tree. It is a wose."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1435
msgid "It looks like it was corrupted too. That's why it is attacking us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1458
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1468
msgid "Trolls! Again?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1462
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1472
msgid "I thought we left them behind us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1482
msgid "Those are not the same."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1486
msgid ""
"The ones we left behind where cave trolls. These ones have always lived here."
" "
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1490
msgid "There are not many of them, but they can be dangerous to travelers anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1588
msgid "The guardian is dead. We should be able to purify the temple now."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1593
msgid "We need to find the altar, and place the artifact on it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1612
msgid "We first need to defeat the guardian to purify the temple."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1621
msgid "That's it, the temple is purified."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1628
msgid ""
"The front of the altar opened when I placed the artifact on it. There is a "
"treasure in it. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1632
msgid "This might be useful for our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1636
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1666
msgid ""
"It looks like the goblin is not in this part of the swamp. Let's go further "
"in."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1640
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1670
msgid "<span font-style='italic'>To himself</span> I hope he is indeed in the swamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1700
msgid "You look badly hurt. What happened to you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=ofite
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1704
msgid ""
"<span font-style='italic'>dying</span> I am of no importance, only the temple"
" is."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=ofite
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1708
msgid "Please, the temple must be purified. The evil grows stronger every day."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=ofite
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1712
msgid ""
"Take this idol. The temple is in thrall to a malevolent spirit. The idol can "
"break the curse if you place it on the altar."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=ofite
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1716
msgid ""
"I tried once in vain. The presence of a powerful guardian is synonymous with "
"desecration. Please, you must… <span font-style='italic'>dies</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1725
msgid "Poor man."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1729
msgid ""
"He didn't even tell us where the temple is. I guess we will figure out when "
"we find it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1769
msgid "Glorp"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1773
msgid "Oh no! He fell into a pothole."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1779
msgid ""
"These summoners... they are spawning creatures faster than we can kill them. "
"We need to find another way into the swamp."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1798
msgid "Weird. This one looks exactly like the previous one we killed."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1805
msgid "This time I'm sure. I already killed this one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1809
msgid "That's probably not a real animal. The witches there must be summoning them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1813
msgid ""
"Kill the witches before killing the Vine Tigers, otherwise we will never see "
"the end of it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1834
msgid "Look over there! It looks like the witch had a horse."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1838
msgid "Should we take it with us?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1840
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1466
msgid "Yes, we cannot let it die here and we need one."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1861
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:1487
msgid ""
"I am sorry pal, but now that I think about it, I wouldn't know what to do of "
"a horse right now."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1877
msgid "No, leave it be. I don't trust witch horses."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/31_Corrupted_Temple.cfg:1893
msgid "There was a coven in the hut."
msgstr ""

