#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1820
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2312
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2365
