#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1982
msgid "The door also opened."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2342
msgid "The wall was actually a door. There is something inside."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2471
msgid "Look over there. This one looks a bit like a dwarf."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2478
msgid "Kill it! Burn it! Destroy it!!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2482
msgid "The whole place! Make it explode!!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2486
msgid ""
"They look quite dangerous. It might be a good idea to kill the goblins "
"servicing them to prevent them from being repaired."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2512
msgid "Great... Another elevator..."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2516
msgid ""
"I assume this means that we need to go deeper to find the goblin leader. And "
"the staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2536
msgid "Let's go down. We need to find the goblin leader. And the staff."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2548
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the machines here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2572
msgid ""
"It looks like the machines around here stopped. This goblin must have has "
"some king of switch on him."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2576
msgid "We should be able to continue without being attacked from behind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2602
msgid ""
"No sign of the staff. The rumor about the goblins having the staff must have "
"been only a rumor."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:2606
msgid "We need to start again the investigation."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario], id=34_Hive
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:4
msgid "Hive"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:907
msgid ""
"There are a lot of Gobots here. We must be getting close to the goblin "
"leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:911
msgid ""
"From what we know, if we find him, we find the sceptre. Let's start "
"searching."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:941
msgid "It looks like it stopped the leak that was spitting fire from the wall."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:953
msgid "There's a weird-looking borb here. Should I touch it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1008
msgid "It looks like it stopped the leaks that were spitting fire in the room."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1041
msgid "The fire caused by the leaks is back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1515
msgid "That part of the tunnel looks abandoned."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1641
msgid "Isn't that one of those dwarvish teleporter?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1645
msgid ""
"I'm not even angry. \n"
"I'm being so sincere right now. \n"
"Even though it breaks my heart. \n"
"I'll kill them. \n"
"And tear them to pieces. \n"
"And throw every piece into a fire."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1654
msgid ""
"How did they even manage to bring it here? It even seems to work. Or at least"
" it's glowing."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1658
msgid ""
"You all don't realize. It should not even be possible. One should not be able"
" to move those runes without breaking them or the spell. That's not how magic"
" works."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1662
msgid ""
"I mean, it's not like if goblins were well known for using things that can "
"malfunction or explode anytime, right?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1709
msgid "Cursed orcs! Cursed invaders!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1713
msgid "Everything rampaged! Fe’s hordes destroyed! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1724
msgid "Ock not have magical staff! Stupid human mage not have staff! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1770
msgid "Protection staff ours! Goblins! You all pay!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1793
msgid "Me lose but no problem! Ancient evil and humans fight now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Fe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1797
msgid "Goblins look, laugh and take what’s left! Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1820
msgid ""
"There is some kind of force field preventing me from getting closer to the "
"sceptre."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1841
msgid "Here it is. The staff of protection."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1849
msgid ""
"It seems like removing it from its base shut down the complex. At least we "
"won't have to fight those metal things anymore."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1853
msgid "Hurrah! We have saved Idaamub!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1868
msgid "Not so fast young man. I am afraid this goblin gave us dark news."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1872
msgid ""
"I would seem that the Ocks have survived and are trying once again to destroy"
" Idaamub."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1876
msgid ""
"We need to get to the capital and warn the king before it is too late. Our "
"journey has not come to its end yet."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/34_Hive.cfg:1948
msgid ""
"It is so frustrating. I feel we are close to finding the sceptre, but these "
"goblins and their machines won't allow us to get it back."
msgstr ""

