#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:813
msgid "Humans"
msgstr ""

#. [unit], id=trader, type=Rogue
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:661
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2180
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2388
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2608
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35b_Flooded_Tunnels.cfg:2812
msgid "Oddaty, the Scavenger"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:717
msgid ""
"The elevator lead us here. I have no idea were we are. I hope we are no too "
"far from an exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:721
msgid ""
"It looks like there are some machines further, but they don't seem to move. "
"They probably got disabled with the rest of the complex."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:730
msgid "I gonna smash'em."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:795
msgid "There seem to be a lever there. I gonna pull it."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:812
msgid "A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall. It seems I found the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:832
msgid "Pull it please."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:848
msgid "A huge rock slid and opened a hole in the wall."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:852
msgid "It seems we found the exit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:862
msgid "Wait, those are legionaries. Let me talk to them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:886
msgid "Legionary, report!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:890
msgid "The Great Mage!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:894
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:964
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1026
msgid "By Of’s shield, is the Guardian sending you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:898
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:968
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"Actually, we are on a mission for the kingdom, but we might be of mutual "
"help."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:902
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:972
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1034
msgid "Tell me, where are we and what are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:906
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:976
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, we are in the middle of nowhere. Our detachment left Oof "
"fortress to try to get emergency reinforcement from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:910
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:980
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"Four days ago, a necromancer with terrible powers by the name of Isut "
"appeared and fell onto us, flanked by undead and Dunefolk. The Dunefolk "
"outnumbering us, they blocked access to Idaamub’s castle from the east and we"
" got blocked from both sides."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:914
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:984
msgid "That is terrible news."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:918
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:988
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1050
msgid ""
"The six of us left by the old temple road to dodge Isut, but we fell onto one"
" of his tentacle guardians, which did not spare us. We both took refuge here,"
" but it is impossible to bring reinforcement from the legion to captain "
"Soimaql on time."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:922
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:992
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1054
msgid "We might be able to do something about that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:926
msgid ""
"I know who you are, I think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my"
" comrades the boost they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:930
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1000
msgid "Our course of action is clear."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:934
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1004
msgid ""
"We need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's fortress and free it "
"from Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:938
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1008
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1066
msgid "We will then join Idaamub's castle to help break the Dunefolk siege."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:942
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1012
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1070
msgid "Once it is done, we will be able to deliver our message to the king."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:946
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1016
msgid "Stay here to heal your wounds. You will be of no help like that."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:950
msgid "Sir, yes, Sir!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:960
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1022
msgid "Excuse me, sir."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:996
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"I don’t know who you are, but if you’re as competent as you look like, I "
"think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my comrades the boost "
"they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1046
msgid "That's terrible news."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1062
msgid ""
"Well, looks like we need to go down the old temple road to reach Oof's "
"fortress and free it from Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Alealyan
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1093
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/37_Old_Temple.cfg:723
msgid ""
"Those tentacles, those teeth… those flickering lights… and all those dead… "
"why so many dead?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1097
msgid "Looks like he lost his mind."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1111
msgid ""
"Mylord Oddaty and I supplied a group of treasure hunters that were examining "
"the flooded tunnels west. Maybe you are also going in that direction?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1115
msgid "I'm sorry but we aren't."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1119
msgid "They have not come for several days. They never talked about leaving."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1123
msgid ""
"It is always displeasing to lose regular customers, especially when you do "
"not know where they went. If by chance you meet them, tell them we appreciate"
" doing business with them."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1127
msgid ""
"Well, if we happen to meet them, we will tell them you are looking forward "
"seeing them again."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1131
msgid ""
"And if it happens that they… hmm… closed their account, come back to tell us "
"where they are."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1135
msgid ""
"I am sorry, but, even if we were to visit those tunnels, I do not think we "
"would have the time to come back to you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1139
msgid ""
"You would not regret it, I promise. In these difficult times, it would be "
"regrettable to lose their… support."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Oboavlidlu
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"Were I to learn that you go into the tunnels, I would wait for you at their "
"entrance; that way you will not have to come back here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1159
msgid ""
"Come in, come in! Hmm… you do not seem move in the best circles, but one "
"should never under-estimate the lower classes…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1163
msgid ""
"My assistant and I have found these items on a group of mages on the temple "
"road. Some of these items might interest you, but we have not yet got them "
"rid of their… unpleasant smell."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1167
msgid "But it should not disturb someone like you, should it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1208
msgid "What can Oddaty the Scavenger do for you today?"
msgstr ""

