msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=Young Giant Spider LoI, race=monster
#: ./Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Spider.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Although the most encounter version is its adult form, Giant Spider are not "
"born directly as such. When they are born, they are called Spiderlings and "
"have a size similar to Giant Scorpions. They then metamorphose a first time "
"to become what we call Young Giant Spiders, that are twice the size of the "
"Spiderling, then a second time to become Giant Spiders. Although its younger "
"version tend to hide from sight, it is a formidable opponent that should not "
"be taken lightly."
msgstr ""

